graph TD
    User([End User]) --> |Prompt| ClientApp[Client Application]
    
    subgraph Myelin Sentinel [Myelin Sentinel Agent]
        direction TB
        Proxy[Gateway/Proxy Interceptor]
        AgentCore[Agent Remediation Brain]
        BgWorker[24/7 Background Observer]
        
        Proxy --> |Check Request| AgentCore
        AgentCore --> |Rewrite if Bad| Proxy
    end
    
    ClientApp --> |OpenAI/LLM REST Call| Proxy
    Proxy --> |Forward Clean Prompt| LLM((LLMs: OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama))
    LLM --> |Raw Response| Proxy
    
    Proxy -.-> |Async Dispatch| BgWorker
    
    subgraph Myelin 5 Pillars [Myelin Engine]
        F[Fairness]
        B[Bias]
        FC[FCAM]
        T[Toxicity]
        G[Governance]
    end
    
    AgentCore <--> |Audit| F & B & FC & T & G
    BgWorker <--> |Deep Audit| F & B & FC & T & G
    
    BgWorker --> |Alerts & Analytics| Dashboard[Admin Dashboard / Slack Alerts]
